Package de.wi08e.myhome.frontend.exceptions

Exception Summary
FrontendException  
LoginUsernameOrPasswordWrong This exception is raised when the username is wrong, non-existend or does not match the given password
NoAdminRights Raised when an operation requires admin-rights, which the given user does not possess
NotLoggedIn Raised when given userToken is not valid.
PasswordTooShort This exception is thrown when a password is too short
UsernameAlreadyInUse This exception is thrown when the username is already used by someone else
UsernameTooShortOrInvalid This exception is thrown when an username is too short
UserNotFound This exception is raised when a requested username is not found.
